msg: Document the side effect of discover_changed_paths with svn_client_mergeinfo_log2()
(svn_client_mergeinfo_log2): The revisions provided to the receiver is altered
by the discover_changed_paths argument.  As opposed to svn_client_log5()
where it just changes how much info about each revision is provided.
